TY  - JOUR
TI  - Objectives, Constraints, and Outcomes in Optimal Growth Models
AU  - Koopmans, Tjalling C.
AB  - [This paper surveys the results of mostly recent research on optimal aggregate economic growth models, and comments on the difficulties encountered and on desirable directions of further research.]
